data.name: customSqlQuery1.Sql
data.value: select distinct A.LINENAME ,A.맨홀 ,A.지반고 ,A.관저고 , A.지반고 - A.관저고 as 높이 ,(A.지반고 - A.관저고) -0.4 as 내부높이 , A.지반고 - A.관저고 + 0.4 as 터파기높이 ,B.MH_CD as 맨홀코드 , nvl(C.cd_nm, '미등록') as 맨호규격 ,D.cd as 굴착공법코드 ,nvl(D.cd_nm, '미등록') as 굴착공법 ,E.cd as 굴착장비코드 ,nvl(E.CD_NM, '미등록') as 굴착장비 ,F.cd as 포장코드 ,nvl(F.cd_nm, '미등록') as 포장종류 from PIPE01M00 A , (select PROJECT_CD ,LINENAME ,MAX(SEQ) SEQ ,맨홀 from PIPE01M00 where 맨홀 not like 'E1%' and TRIM(맨홀) <> '' group by 맨홀 order by PROJECT_CD, LINENAME, SEQ, 맨홀 ) AA , pipe01m10 B left outer join cod10m00 C on (B.MH_CD = cd and C.mngr_cd = 'MH_CD') left outer join COD10M00 D on (B.PAVE_TYPE_CD = D.cd and D.MNGR_CD = 'PAVE_TYPE') left outer join COD10M00 E on (B.BH_CD = E.CD and E.mngr_cd = 'BH_CD') left outer join COD10M00 F on (B.PAVE_CD = F.CD and F.mngr_cd = 'PAVE_CD') where A.PROJECT_CD = @P_PROJECT_CD and TRIM(A.맨홀) <> '' and A.PROJECT_CD = B.PROJECT_CD and A.LINENAME = B.LINENAME and A.SEQ = B.SEQ and AA.PROJECT_CD = A.PROJECT_CD and AA.LINENAME = A.LINENAME and AA.SEQ = A.SEQ and A.맨홀 not like 'E1%'

data.name: customSqlQuery2.Sql
data.value: select CONCAT('TYPE ', XX.ROWID) TYPE_CD , XX.BH_CD , XX.굴착장비 , XX.MH_CD , XX.맨홀규격 , XX.PAVE_TYPE_CD , XX.굴착공법 , XX.PAVE_CD , XX.포장종류 , XX.관경 , XX.높이평균 , XX.수량 , XX.ROWID from ( select x.bh_cd , aa.cd_nm as 굴착장비 , x.mh_cd , bb.cd_nm as 맨홀규격 , x.pave_type_cd , cc.cd_nm as 굴착공법 , x.pave_cd , dd.cd_nm as 포장종류 , x.관경 , x.높이평균 , x.cnt as 수량 , row_number() over( order by x.bh_cd, x.mh_cd, x.pave_type_cd, x.pave_cd) as rowid from ( select b.BH_CD ,b.MH_CD ,b.PAVE_TYPE_CD ,b.PAVE_CD ,a.관경 , round(avg(a.지반고 - a.관저고- 0.4), 2) 높이평균 ,count(*) cnt from pipe01m00 a, pipe01m10 b where a.PROJECT_Cd = @P_PROJECT_CD and a.PROJECT_CD = b.PROJECT_CD and a.LINENAME = b.LINENAME and a.SEQ = b.SEQ group by b.BH_CD , b.MH_CD , b.PAVE_TYPE_CD, b.PAVE_CD , a.관경 ) x , cod10m00 aa , cod10m00 bb , cod10m00 cc , cod10m00 dd where aa.mngr_cd = 'BH_CD' and aa.cd = x.bh_cd and bb.mngr_cd = 'MH_CD' and bb.cd = x.mh_cd and cc.mngr_cd = 'PAVE_TYPE' and cc.cd = x.pave_type_cd and dd.mngr_cd = 'PAVE_CD' and dd.cd = x.pave_cd ) XX

data.name: customSqlQuery3.Sql
data.value: select distinct XX.맨홀규격 , xx.굴착공법 , XX.굴착장비 , XX.BH_CD , XX.MH_CD , xx.pave_type_cd , xx.rowid from ( select x.bh_cd , aa.cd_nm as 굴착장비 , x.mh_cd , bb.cd_nm as 맨홀규격 , x.pave_type_cd , cc.cd_nm as 굴착공법 , x.pave_cd , dd.cd_nm as 포장종류 , x.관경 , x.높이평균 , x.cnt as 수량 , row_number() over( order by x.bh_cd, x.mh_cd, x.pave_type_cd, x.pave_cd) as rowid from ( select b.BH_CD ,b.MH_CD ,b.PAVE_TYPE_CD ,b.PAVE_CD ,a.관경 , round(avg(a.지반고 - a.관저고- 0.4), 2) 높이평균 ,count(*) cnt from pipe01m00 a, pipe01m10 b where a.PROJECT_Cd = @P_PROJECT_CD and a.PROJECT_CD = b.PROJECT_CD and a.LINENAME = b.LINENAME and a.SEQ = b.SEQ group by b.BH_CD , b.MH_CD , b.PAVE_TYPE_CD, b.PAVE_CD , a.관경 ) x , cod10m00 aa , cod10m00 bb , cod10m00 cc , cod10m00 dd where aa.mngr_cd = 'BH_CD' and aa.cd = x.bh_cd and bb.mngr_cd = 'MH_CD' and bb.cd = x.mh_cd and cc.mngr_cd = 'PAVE_TYPE' and cc.cd = x.pave_type_cd and dd.mngr_cd = 'PAVE_CD' and dd.cd = x.pave_cd ) XX order by xx.rowid

data.name: customSqlQuery4.Sql
data.value: SELECT B.PROJECT_CD , B.P_MNGR_CD , B.P_CD , C.CD_NM 맨홀규격 , B.MNGR_CD , B.CD , D.CD_NM 구조물 , B.CD_VAL 구조물규격 FROM ( SELECT X.PROJECT_CD , ROW_NUMBER() OVER( ORDER BY X.PROJECT_CD) AS ROWID FROM ( SELECT DISTINCT PROJECT_CD FROM COD11T00 WHERE PROJECT_CD = @P_PROJECT_CD UNION ALL SELECT DISTINCT PROJECT_CD FROM COD11T00 WHERE PROJECT_CD = 'XXXXXXXXXX' ) X ) A, COD11T00 B, COD10M00 C, COD10M00 D WHERE A.ROWID = 1 AND A.PROJECT_CD = B.PROJECT_CD AND B.P_MNGR_CD = 'MH_CD' AND B.P_CD = @P_P_CD AND B.P_MNGR_CD = C.MNGR_CD AND B.P_CD = C.CD AND B.MNGR_CD = D.MNGR_CD AND B.CD = D.CD

data.name: customSqlQuery5.Sql
data.value: SELECT B.PROJECT_CD , B.P_MNGR_CD , B.P_CD , C.CD_NM 포장명 , B.MNGR_CD , B.CD , D.CD_NM 포장구성 , B.CD_VAL 규격 FROM ( SELECT X.PROJECT_CD , ROW_NUMBER() OVER( ORDER BY X.PROJECT_CD) AS ROWID FROM ( SELECT DISTINCT PROJECT_CD FROM COD13T00 WHERE PROJECT_CD = @P_PROJECT_CD UNION ALL SELECT DISTINCT PROJECT_CD FROM COD13T00 WHERE PROJECT_CD = 'XXXXXXXXXX' ) X ) A, COD13T00 B, COD10M00 C, COD10M00 D WHERE A.ROWID = 1 AND A.PROJECT_CD = B.PROJECT_CD AND B.P_MNGR_CD = 'PAVE_CD' AND B.P_MNGR_CD = C.MNGR_CD AND B.P_CD = C.CD AND B.MNGR_CD = D.MNGR_CD AND B.CD = D.CD ORDER BY B.P_MNGR_CD, B.P_CD, B.CD

data.name: customSqlQuery6.Sql
data.value: SELECT B.PROJECT_CD , B.P_MNGR_CD , B.P_CD , C.CD_NM 관로 , B.MNGR_CD , B.CD , D.CD_NM 관로구성 , B.CD_VAL 규격 FROM ( SELECT X.PROJECT_CD , ROW_NUMBER() OVER( ORDER BY X.PROJECT_CD) AS ROWID FROM ( SELECT DISTINCT PROJECT_CD FROM COD12T00 WHERE PROJECT_CD = @P_PROJECT_CD UNION ALL SELECT DISTINCT PROJECT_CD FROM COD12T00 WHERE PROJECT_CD = 'XXXXXXXXXX' ) X ) A, COD12T00 B, COD10M00 C, COD10M00 D WHERE A.ROWID = 1 AND A.PROJECT_CD = B.PROJECT_CD AND B.P_MNGR_CD = 'PIPE_ROAD' AND B.P_MNGR_CD = C.MNGR_CD AND B.P_CD = C.CD AND B.MNGR_CD = D.MNGR_CD AND B.CD = D.CD ORDER BY B.P_MNGR_CD, B.P_CD, B.CD
